CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 7, 1964, pg. 7, reads: "Mr. and Mrs. Charles Golphin...recently married"
TitMainTitle: Bride wearing gown with lace overlay and mid length veil, feeding cake to groom Charles Golphin wearing bow tie and jacket with satin lapels in interior with twisted crepe paper streamers
